To get the latest head of CVS tree:

cvs -d:pserver:anonymous@process-getopt.cvs.sourceforge.net:/cvsroot/process-getopt login
 
cvs -z3 -d:pserver:anonymous@process-getopt.cvs.sourceforge.net:/cvsroot/process-getopt co -P process-getopt

argp and goptions are C versions of this which understand similar commands eg
add_opt and wrap around glibc's argp and glib's g_option_context_parse. The later
is rather weak in that is not able to format long option descriptions. Of course,
they are both much faster than process-getopt.
